{"word":"σκιαγραφία","slug":"σκιαγραφία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n94818\" key=\"skiagrafi/a\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">σκῐᾱγρᾰφ-ία</orth>, <gen lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gen\">ἡ</gen>, <sense id=\"n94818.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">painting with the shadows</tr_> (cf. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σκιαγραφέω</foreign>), <pb n=\"1610\" TEIform=\"pb\"/> so as to produce an illusion of solidity at a distance, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">scene-painting</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ς. ἀσαφεῖ καὶ ἀπατηλῷ χρώμεθα</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg032:107d\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Criti.\">Criti.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">107d</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">σκιαγραφίαν ἀρετῆς περιγραπτέον</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg030.perseus-grc1:365c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ R.\">R.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">365c</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg030.perseus-grc1:602d\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">602d</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg004.perseus-grc1:69b\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Phd.\">Phd.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">69b</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Numen.</author> </bibl> ap. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2018.tlg001:14:5\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Eus.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">PE</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">14.5</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg2018.tlg001:26\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">26</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἡ ς. καὶ τὰ ἐνύπνια</foreign>, compared as being both illusory, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg025.perseus-grc1:1024b:23\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Metaph.\">Metaph.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1024b23</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἡ δημηγορικὴ λέξις ἔοικε τῇ ς.</foreign>, i.e. in being calculated for effect, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg038.perseus-grc1:1414a:8\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Rh.\">Rh.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1414a8</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0385.tlg001:52:7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.C.\">D.C.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">52.7</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}